column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.devRad_u, p.devRadErr_u, p.expRad_u, p.expRadErr_u, p.fracDeV_u, m.re_kpc, g.lgm_tot_p5#, m.log_Mass, m.e_log_Mass, p.z, p.run, p.rerun, p.field, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, s.mjd FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN galSpecExtra AS g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid JOIN mangaPipe3D AS m on m.specobjid = s.specobjid WHERE s.class = galaxy
